(3004, 2, '2017-02-18 19:00:13', '2017-02-18 19:00:13', '<h6>Myself on the approach with the backside of Torreys (the tuning forks) in the background. (Photo: <a href="https://www.instagram.com/303zachary/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Zach Cohen</a>)<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3079" src="https://charlesstemen.test/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_0398.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="1603" /></h6>\r\n<h6>Our first view of Dead Dog. Holy hell.<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3083" src="https://charlesstemen.test/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_3164.jpg" alt="" width="2193" height="1910" /></h6>\r\n<h6>My line in red, Zachs in yellow.<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3086" src="https://charlesstemen.test/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_3164_Route.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="1525" /></h6>\r\n<h6> Myself on the final steps to the summit. (Photo: <a href="https://www.instagram.com/303zachary/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Zach Cohen</a>)<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3080" src="https://charlesstemen.test/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_0402.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="1125" /></h6>\r\n<h6>Zach cheesin w/ some bloody teeth :)<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3082" src="https://charlesstemen.test/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_1673.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="1125" /></h6>\r\n<h6>Gopro Screenshot from the peak looking down. Dead Dog is out of sight to the left under the cliff.<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3078" src="https://charlesstemen.test/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/91630DC1-CA79-48F5-AA5E-0047ADD68329.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="1125" /></h6>\r\n<h6>In the couloir:<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3077" src="https://charlesstemen.test/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/76821DC9-7775-47BA-90C4-D5D3E5844BA9.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="1125" /></h6>\r\n<h6>(Photo: <a href="https://www.instagram.com/303zachary/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Zach Cohen</a>)<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3081" src="https://charlesstemen.test/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_0403.jpg" alt="" width="3024" height="3063" /></h6>', 'TORREYS PEAK - DEAD DOG COULOIR', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'torreys-peak-dead-dog-couloir', '', '', '2017-12-25 15:56:33', '2017-12-25 15:56:33', '', 0, 'http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/?p=3004', 0, 'post', '', 0) ;
