(3005, 2, '2017-09-30 17:33:15', '2017-09-30 17:33:15', 'After September graced the front range peaks with some snow, <a href="https://www.instagram.com/303zachary/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Zach Cohen</a> &amp; I headed up Kelso Ridge for some spicy, snowy, icy &amp; wet 3rd/4th class scrambling. We didn\'t do a great job at photographing the crux sections. We were probably too puckered.\r\n<h6>Grays Peak on the left, Torreys on the Right. Kelso Ridge is the ridgeline straight up from the photo on the right.<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3056" src="https://charlesstemen.test/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_8325.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="1125" /></h6>\r\n<h6>Looks Badass:<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3057" src="https://charlesstemen.test/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_8327.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="795" /></h6>\r\n<h6>Zach topping out on one of the more 5thish class sections:<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3058" src="https://charlesstemen.test/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_8334.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="2000" /></h6>\r\n<h6>Myself ascending a snowier section of the route: (photo:<a href="https://www.instagram.com/303zachary/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> Zach Cohen</a>)<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3055" src="https://charlesstemen.test/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_0912.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="1816" /></h6>\r\n<h6>Zach topping out on another fun scramble with Grays in the background:<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3059" src="https://charlesstemen.test/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_8339.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1129" /></h6>\r\n<h6>Zach approaching the crux:<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3060" src="https://charlesstemen.test/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_8340.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="2000" /></h6>\r\n<h6>View from the summit with Grays Peak in the foreground.<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3061" src="http://charlesstemen.test/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_8344.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="937" /></h6>', 'TORREYS PEAK - KELSO RIDGE', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'torreys-peak-kelso-ridge', '', '', '2017-12-23 19:27:08', '2017-12-23 19:27:08', '', 0, 'http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/?p=3005', 0, 'post', '', 0),
